%% Diagram: Component overview — read and lifecycle path
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    CLIENTS["Clients<br/>browser · CLI · SDK"]
    CDN["CDN<br/>immutable cache"]
    LB["Load balancer"]
    ROUTER["API router"]
    READ["Paste Read Service"]
    EXPIRY["Expiration sweeper"]
    ABUSE["Abuse detection"]

    subgraph Storage["Storage tier"]
        REDIS["Redis cluster"]
        PG[("PostgreSQL")]
        S3["Object storage"]
    end

    CLIENTS --> CDN -->|miss| LB --> ROUTER --> READ
    READ --> REDIS
    READ -->|cache miss| PG
    READ -->|cache miss| S3
    EXPIRY --> REDIS
    EXPIRY --> PG
    EXPIRY --> S3
    ABUSE --> REDIS
